docs.lead_paragraph: FOR the Hundred Neediest Cases of New York City, THE NEW YORK TIMES today makes its thirty-ninth annual appeal. Here on these pages are told the stories of the Neediest--stories of sickness and heartache, of mistrust, of friendless childhood and helpless old age.
